data.description: Welcome home to this delightful 4-bed, 2-bath haven w/fenced yard, offering the perfect blend of comfort & charm! Revel in the convenience of a single attached garage and a bonus detached 2-car deep garage - ample space for your vehicles and hobbies. Step into a kitchen that's not just stylish but functionally equipped with all the appliances you need. The combo dining room, adorned w/sliding doors, seamlessly connects indoor & outdoor living. Laundry becomes less of a chore w/hook-ups both up & down.  Brand-new roof in 2023 ensures worry-free living for years to come. Revel in the convenience of a single attached garage and a bonus detached 2-car deep garage - ample space for your vehicles and hobbies. Ring security items included.
